      <title>摩根士丹利提拔 Mahdavi 和 Teasdale 负责美洲并购业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/morgan-stanley-promotes-mahdavi-teasdale-to-run-americas-m-a</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，摩根士丹利已提拔 Lily Mahdavi 和 Ben Teasdale 共同领导其美洲区并购团队。]]></description>
