      <title>爱尔兰主要政党达成联盟协议以保留权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/ireland-s-fianna-fail-fine-gael-reach-government-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过数周的谈判，爱尔兰两大主要政党达成新的联合执政协议，将再次执政五年。]]></description>
